  • Databases: PostgreSQL, MySQL, Oracle, MongoDB
  • Frameworks: Spring, Spring Boot, NodeJS, React, Django, Express, Ruby on Rails
  • Tools: Git, AWS(S3, ElasticBeanstalk, Lambda), VMware, Heroku
